'''第一次哈馬戰役'''（'''1st Hama offensive'''）是一場於[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]期間的軍事行動，在2012年12月16日爆發，引起方為敘利亞的反對派武裝力量[[自由敘利亞軍|自由敘利亞軍]]。本次戰役雙方的主要目的是為了控制敘利亞中西部的[[哈馬省|哈馬省]]，而最終戰役在[[敘利亞武裝部隊|敘利亞政府軍]]的反擊後結束，反對派僅奪下哈馬省北部的幾個城鎮與村莊。 

== 背景 ==
在哈馬省主要受到政府方掌控的狀況之下，為了切斷在[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]的政府軍主要補給路線，反對勢力自由敘利亞軍試圖攻下哈馬省以及首府[[哈馬_(敘利亞)|哈馬]]，而在2012年12月16日開始進行攻擊。

== 進攻行動 ==
哈馬省的反對勢力在2012年12月16日開始進攻，並給予當地政府軍隊最後通牒，要求48小時內投降。<ref name="aleppo pm">{{cite news|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/12/17/255673.html|title=Syria's PM in first Aleppo visit since outbreak of fighting|last=[[法新社|法新社]]|date=2012-12-17|publisher=Al-Arabiya|accessdate=2012-12-19|archive-date=2017-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009223703/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/12/17/255673.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在這兩天之內，[[敘利亞人權觀察團|敘利亞人權觀察團]]（SOHR）與[[自由敘利亞軍|自由敘利亞軍]]的軍事指揮官Qassem Saadeddine宣稱，政府軍已喪失對城鎮哈法雅（Halfaya）、卡法納布達（Kafr Nabudah）、哈雅林（Hayalin）、哈斯拉雅（Hasraya）、艾拉塔明（al-Lataminah）、泰伊巴特艾伊曼（Taybat al-Imam）和卡法塞達（Kafr Zita）的控制，哈馬省西部農村及哈馬北方落入反對勢力手中。<ref name="sohr1">{{cite web|url=http://www.facebook.com/syriaohr/posts/310435475731464|title=Hama Province|last=SOHR|publisher=Facebook|accessdate=2012-12-19}}</ref><ref name="battlefor">{{cite web |url=http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2012/12/18/syria-live-coverage-a-battle-for-hama.html |title=Syria Live Coverage: A Battle for Hama? |publisher=Enduringamerica.com |date=2012-12-18 |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2017-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011112902/http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2012/12/18/syria-live-coverage-a-battle-for-hama.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RebelsSeizeTowns">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/19/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8AJ1FK20121219|title=Rebels seize towns in central Syria|agency=路透社|date=2012-12-19|accessdate=2012-12-20|archive-date=2012-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121219142936/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/19/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8AJ1FK20121219|dead-url=no}}</ref>而反對勢力從[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]的[[邁阿賴努阿曼|邁阿賴努阿曼]]和（Maarrat al-Nu'man）和[[吉斯爾舒古爾|吉斯爾舒古爾]]（Jisr ash-Shugour）向南推進{{convert|40|km|mi}}後，遇到小抵抗。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/dec/18/syria-conflict-kidnappings-yarmouk-camp-damascus-live#block-50d08c71b5793fbbacbc4f40|title=Rebel gains (3.32 pm GMT)|date=2012-12-18|work=Middle East Liveblog|accessdate=2012-12-19|archive-date=2012-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121219032345/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/dec/18/syria-conflict-kidnappings-yarmouk-camp-damascus-live#block-50d08c71b5793fbbacbc4f40|dead-url=no}}</ref>反對勢力似乎在48小時內超越了哈馬北方的軍事線進行軍事行動，<ref name="battlefor"/> 而坎謝克亨（Khan Shaykhun）及瑪哈德（Mhardeh）也都遭受攻擊。<ref name="aleppo pm"/>

反對派宣稱，哈馬市內部也發生了戰鬥。國際分析師則想了解是否軍隊前進[[霍姆斯_(敘利亞)|霍姆斯]]和[[拉塔基亞|拉塔基亞]]時重新部署，但未被證實。<ref name="battlefor"/><ref name="RebelsSeizeTowns"/>

12月19日，根據[[地方協調委員會|地方協調委員會]]（LCC），安全部隊在哈雅林外設立檢查關卡，引起外界懷疑是否完全控制哈雅林，而不像其他所攻占的地方一樣狀況。<ref>Miller, James. [http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2012/12/19/syria-live-coverage-the-insurgents-close-on-hama.html "Syria Live Coverage: The Insurgents Close on Hama"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2012/12/19/syria-live-coverage-the-insurgents-close-on-hama.html |date=20171019084135 }}. Enduringamerica.com. 2012-12-19.</ref>

12月20日，反對勢力攻下村莊摩克（Morek），並包圍[[阿拉維派|阿拉維派]]的城鎮瑪恩（Maan）與艾特雷沙（al-Tleisa）。<ref>{{cite web |last=Karouny |first=Mariam |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/12/20/uk-syria-crisis-idUKBRE8BI1JT20121220 |title=Syrian rebels fight for strategic town in Hama province |agency=路透社 |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2013-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130212060610/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/12/20/uk-syria-crisis-idUKBRE8BI1JT20121220 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月23日，LCC和SOHR表示多達300位平民在麵包店前排隊時被戰機轟炸而死亡。<ref>{{cite web |author=<!--[if IE 6]> <![endif]--> |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/12/23/256715.html |title=At least 300 killed in regime airstrike near Syrian bakery |publisher=Al Arabiya |date=2012-12-23 |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206074546/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/12/23/256715.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>敘利亞政府方證實許多婦孺因轟炸死亡，但也指責反對勢力的進攻。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2012/12/24/syria-live-coverage-94-killed-in-regime-airstrike-on-bakery.html |title=Syria Live Coverage: "94 Killed" in Regime Airstrike on Bakery Queue |publisher=Enduringamerica.com |date=2012-12-24 |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2017-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009233838/http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2012/12/24/syria-live-coverage-94-killed-in-regime-airstrike-on-bakery.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月26日，政府軍擊退已經進入村莊內的反對方，收復三個阿拉維派的村莊，包括瑪恩在內。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-12-27/head-of-syrian-military-police-defects/4444332 |title=Syria's top military policeman switches sides |publisher=[[澳洲廣播公司|ABC]] |date=2012-12-27 |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019083802/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-12-27/head-of-syrian-military-police-defects/4444332 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月29日，卡法納布達有六人因空襲死亡，包括兩名孩童和兩名女人。另外，在泰伊巴特艾伊曼也有一人死於轟炸。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.facebook.com/syriaohr/posts/370628119700477 |title=Hama: 6 people were killed by the airforce bombardment on the town of Kafarnbouda |publisher=Facebook |date=2012-12-30 }}</ref>

12月30日，政府軍的普通指揮官宣布收復具有戰略性的村莊摩克。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2012-12/31/c_124168491.htm |title=Syrian troops regain control of central town in Aleppo |agency=[[新華網|新華網]] |date=2012-12-31 |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2013-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104191137/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2012-12/31/c_124168491.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月31日，軍隊在哈法雅進行轟炸。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nation.com.pk/pakistan-news-newspaper-daily-english-online/international/01-Jan-2013/syria-backs-plans-to-end-conflict |title=Syria backs plans to end conflict |work=The Nation |location=巴基斯坦 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103204204/http://www.nation.com.pk/pakistan-news-newspaper-daily-english-online/international/01-Jan-2013/syria-backs-plans-to-end-conflict |archivedate=2013-01-03 }}</ref>

== 後續 ==
2013年1月21日，SOHR表示發生在哈馬東部郊區的一個親政府的民兵組織總部，發生[[汽車炸彈|汽車炸彈]]攻擊，造成50人喪生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/22/world/middleeast/syria-war-developments.html?hpw&_r=0 |title=Moscow Is Sending Planes to Lebanon for 100 Russians Leaving Syria |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2017-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812063502/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/22/world/middleeast/syria-war-developments.html?hpw&_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1月22日，政府方為了奪回失去的哈馬省北部，再度展開攻勢。政府軍動用了1,500名士兵與100輛坦克，重點攻擊瑪哈德區的奇蘭茲（Karnaz），此處部署了1,000名的反對勢力。二月初，有新聞報導指出反對勢力擔心失去奇蘭茲以及相關的卡法布納達，進而扭轉先前奪得哈馬省北部領土的局勢。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mcclatchydc.com/2013/02/01/181784/syrian-government-offensive-forces.html |title=Syrian government offensive forces thousands to find shelter in caves, cars |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025145233/http://www.mcclatchydc.com/2013/02/01/181784/syrian-government-offensive-forces.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月6日，54名從事國防相關的政府職員在哈馬附近的艾巴克（al-Buraq），因為一台小巴士在公車站爆炸而喪生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://world.time.com/2013/02/08/group-says-54-died-in-syria-military-factory-blast/ |title=Group Says 54 Died in Syria Military Factory Blast |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2020-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200214031124/https://world.time.com/2013/02/08/group-says-54-died-in-syria-military-factory-blast/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月7日，政府軍在16天的戰鬥之後，奪回奇蘭茲。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130207/syria-regime-retakes-town-damascus-clashes-rage-0 |title=Syria regime retakes town as Damascus clashes rage |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045854/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130207/syria-regime-retakes-town-damascus-clashes-rage-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在兩天前，政府軍也收復了附近的城鎮穆希爾（Mughir），確保哈馬省西部阿拉維派村莊的走廊地帶。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-1-158795-Syrian-troops-capture-Karnaz |title=''Syrian troops capture Karnaz'' (巴基斯坦新聞) |accessdate=2013-04-07 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025190403/http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-1-158795-Syrian-troops-capture-Karnaz |dead-url=no }}</ref>

